    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  InlineDynamicTypeBuilder.TargetHandler.Prepared.ForRebaseInstrumentation
      A prepared target handler for an instrumentation that creates a redefinition of the given type by rebasing the original code of redefined method and by invoking these methods when a super method should be invoked.
      static class  InlineDynamicTypeBuilder.TargetHandler.Prepared.ForRedefinitionInstrumentation
      A prepared target handler for an instrumentation that creates a redefinition of the given type by invoking the actual super method when redefining a method.
